<lb n="0769a15" ed="T"/><head type="no">No. 500</head>
<lb n="0769a16" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><note n="0769002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（佛說）＋羅【三】【宮】</note><note n="0769002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（佛說）＋羅【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769002"><lem wit="【大】">羅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">佛說羅</rdg></app>云忍辱經</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0769a17" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0769a18" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0769a19" ed="T"/><byline type="Translator">西晉沙門<note n="0769003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（釋）＋法炬【三】【宮】</note><note n="0769003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（釋）＋法炬【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769003"><lem wit="【大】">法炬</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">釋法炬</rdg></app>譯</byline>
<lb n="0769a20" ed="T"/><div1 type="jing"><p id="pT14p0769a2001">阿難曰。吾從佛聞如是。一時佛在舍衛國。祇
<lb n="0769a21" ed="T"/>樹給孤獨園。時<note n="0769004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">鶖露＝秋露【宋】【宮】＊，鶖鷺【元】【明】＊</note><note n="0769004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">鶖露＝秋露【宋】【宮】＊，＝鶖鷺【元】【明】＊</note><app n="0769004"><lem wit="【大】">鶖露</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">秋露</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">鶖鷺</rdg></app>子與羅云俱。以平旦
<lb n="0769a22" ed="T"/>著衣法服。執持應器。入城求食。時<note n="0769005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔有〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0769005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔有〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769005"><lem wit="【大】">有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>輕薄
<lb n="0769a23" ed="T"/>者。<note n="0769006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">逢＝遙【三】【宮】</note><note n="0769006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">逢＝遙【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769006"><lem wit="【大】">逢</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">遙</rdg></app>見兩賢。意念曰。瞿曇沙門。第一弟子。
<lb n="0769a24" ed="T"/>與羅云分<note n="0769007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">衛＝請【三】【宮】</note><note n="0769007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">衛＝請【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769007"><lem wit="【大】">衛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">請</rdg></app>。即興毒意。取地沙土。著<app source="0769004" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">鶖
<lb n="0769a25" ed="T"/>露</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">秋露</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">鶖鷺</rdg></app>子&CB00425;中。擊羅云首。師見羅云。血流污面。
<lb n="0769a26" ed="T"/>師曰。為<note n="0769008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔佛〕－【宮】</note><app n="0769008"><lem wit="【大】">佛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>弟子。慎無含毒。當以慈心愍傷
<lb n="0769a27" ed="T"/>眾生。世尊常云。忍者最快。唯慧者能<note n="0769009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">吾聞佛戒＝聞佛說誡【三】【宮】</note><note n="0769009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">吾聞佛戒＝聞佛說誡【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769009"><lem wit="【大】">吾聞
<lb n="0769a28" ed="T"/>佛戒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">聞佛說誡</rdg></app>。終身不<note n="0769010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">犯＝邪【三】【宮】</note><note n="0769010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">犯＝邪【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769010"><lem wit="【大】">犯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">邪</rdg></app>。吾自攝心。以忍為寶。恣
<lb n="0769a29" ed="T"/>心履惡。猶自投火。貢高自見。愚者謂健。不
<pb n="0769b" id="T14.0500.0769b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0769b01" ed="T"/>計殃禍當還害已。恣心之禍重於須<note n="0769011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">彌＋（首戴須彌）【元】【明】</note><app n="0769011"><lem wit="【大】">彌</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">彌首戴須彌</rdg></app>。畢
<lb n="0769b02" ed="T"/>已年壽。以當惡罪。十六分中未<note n="0769012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">減＝滅【三】【宮】</note><note n="0769012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">減＝滅【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769012"><lem wit="【大】">減</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">滅</rdg></app>其一。愚
<lb n="0769b03" ed="T"/>人作行惡。<note n="0769013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔向〕－【宋】【宮】</note><app n="0769013"><lem wit="【大】">向</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>清淨持戒沙門。猶若逆風把
<lb n="0769b04" ed="T"/>炬火行。狂愚不捨。必自燒身。弊人懷毒。自
<lb n="0769b05" ed="T"/>以為慧。如比丘<note n="0769014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">怙＝怗【宋】，沾【元】【明】【宮】</note><note n="0769014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">怙＝怗【宋】，＝沾【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769014"><lem wit="【大】">怙</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">怗</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】【宮】">沾</rdg></app>沙門四道。為佛弟子。常
<lb n="0769b06" ed="T"/>當伏心。惡<note n="0769015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">生＝至【三】【宮】</note><note n="0769015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">生＝至【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769015"><lem wit="【大】">生</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">至</rdg></app>即滅。勇中之上。天神帝王。雖
<lb n="0769b07" ed="T"/>謂多力。不如忍惡。其力無上。羅云見血流
<lb n="0769b08" ed="T"/>下交面。臨水澡血。而自說曰。我痛斯須。<note n="0769016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">奈＝念【三】【宮】</note><note n="0769016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">奈＝念【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769016"><lem wit="【大】">奈</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">念</rdg></app>
<lb n="0769b09" ed="T"/>彼長苦斯人惡<note n="0769017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔也〕－【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0769017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔也〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0769017"><lem wit="【大】">也</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>。斯地亦惡。<note n="0769018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">余＝奈【三】【宮】</note><note n="0769018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">余＝奈【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769018"><lem wit="【大】">余</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">奈</rdg></app>無慍心悲
<lb n="0769b10" ed="T"/>奈彼何。佛是吾尊。教吾大慈。狂悖之人。志
<lb n="0769b11" ed="T"/>趣凶虐。沙門默忍。以成高德。凶者狼<note n="0769019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">殘＝滅【宋】</note><app n="0769019"><lem wit="【大】">殘</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">滅</rdg></app>。愚
<lb n="0769b12" ed="T"/>人敬焉。沙門守忍。狂愚是輕。斯人惡<app source="0769017" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">也</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>我
<lb n="0769b13" ed="T"/>焉能<note n="0769020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">惡歟＝慈餘【宋】【宮】，慈濟【元】【明】</note><note n="0769020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">惡歟＝慈餘【宋】【宮】，＝慈濟【元】【明】</note><app n="0769020"><lem wit="【大】">惡歟</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">慈餘</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">慈濟</rdg></app>。輪轉無際。豈一<note n="0769021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">向＝面【三】【宮】</note><note n="0769021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">向＝面【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769021"><lem wit="【大】">向</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">面</rdg></app>乎。吾欲以
<lb n="0769b14" ed="T"/>佛至真之經喻誨愚惑。猶以<note n="0769022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔利〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0769022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔利〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769022"><lem wit="【大】">利</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>劍<note n="0769023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">割＝害【宮】</note><app n="0769023"><lem wit="【大】">割</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">害</rdg></app>彼臭
<lb n="0769b15" ed="T"/>屍。屍不知痛。非劍之不利。乃死屍之無知。
<lb n="0769b16" ed="T"/>以天甘露。食彼溷&CB00337;。&CB00337;捨之走。非甘露之
<lb n="0769b17" ed="T"/>不美。乃臭蟲之所不珍矣。以佛真言。訓世
<lb n="0769b18" ed="T"/><note n="0769024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">凶＝嬰【三】【宮】</note><note n="0769024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">凶＝嬰【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769024"><lem wit="【大】">凶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">嬰</rdg></app>愚。不亦然乎。師徒俱還。飯竟澡<note n="0769025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00425;＝浴【三】【宮】</note><note n="0769025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB00425;＝浴【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769025"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00425;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">浴</rdg></app>。洗
<lb n="0769b19" ed="T"/>手漱口。俱到佛所。稽首佛足。<app source="0769004" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">鶖露</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">秋露</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">鶖鷺</rdg></app>子退坐。
<lb n="0769b20" ed="T"/>具以本末。向佛陳之。世尊告曰。夫惡<note n="0769026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔心〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0769026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔心〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769026"><lem wit="【大】">心</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>之
<lb n="0769b21" ed="T"/>興。興<note n="0769027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">己＝已【宮】</note><app n="0769027"><lem wit="【大】">己</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">已</rdg></app>之衰。輕薄者命終。至于夜半。當入
<lb n="0769b22" ed="T"/>無擇地獄之中。獄鬼加痛毒無不至。八萬四
<lb n="0769b23" ed="T"/>千歲。其壽乃終。魂神更受含毒<note n="0769028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">蟒＝蝮【宋】，蛟【元】【明】【宮】</note><note n="0769028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">蟒＝蝮【宋】，＝蛟【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769028"><lem wit="【大】">蟒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">蝮</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】【宮】">蛟</rdg></app>身。毒重
<lb n="0769b24" ed="T"/>還害其身。終而復始。續受<note n="0769029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">蝮＝蟒【三】【宮】</note><note n="0769029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">蝮＝蟒【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769029"><lem wit="【大】">蝮</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">蟒</rdg></app>形。常食<note n="0769030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">沙＝地【三】【宮】</note><note n="0769030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">沙＝地【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769030"><lem wit="【大】">沙</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">地</rdg></app>
<lb n="0769b25" ed="T"/>土。萬歲乃畢。以瞋恚意。向持戒人。故受毒
<lb n="0769b26" ed="T"/>身。以沙土投&CB00425;中。故世世食沙土。而死罪
<lb n="0769b27" ed="T"/>畢乃出。得生為人母懷之時。常有重病。家
<lb n="0769b28" ed="T"/>中日耗。生兒頑鈍。都無手足。其親驚<note n="0769031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">怪＝怖【三】【宮】</note><note n="0769031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">怪＝怖【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769031"><lem wit="【大】">怪</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">怖</rdg></app>。宗
<lb n="0769b29" ed="T"/>家皆然。曰斯何<note n="0769032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">妖＋（怪）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0769032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">妖＋（怪）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769032"><lem wit="【大】">妖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">妖怪</rdg></app>。<note n="0769033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">來＝當【三】【宮】</note><note n="0769033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">來＝當【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769033"><lem wit="【大】">來</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">當</rdg></app>為不祥。即取捐之。
<pb n="0769c" id="T14.0500.0769c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0769c01" ed="T"/>著于四衢路。人往來無不<note n="0769034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">愕＝釋【宋】【宮】</note><app n="0769034"><lem wit="【大】">愕</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">釋</rdg></app>然。<note n="0769035" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔或以瓦石擲〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0769035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔或以瓦石擲〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769035"><lem wit="【大】">或以瓦石
<lb n="0769c02" ed="T"/>擲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>。或以刀杖。皆擊其頭。<note n="0769036" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">蹈＝陷【元】【明】</note><app n="0769036"><lem wit="【大】">蹈</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">陷</rdg></app>腦窮苦。旬月
<lb n="0769c03" ed="T"/>乃死。死後魂神即復更生。輒無手足。<note n="0769037" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">頑鈍＝殘頑【三】【宮】</note><note n="0769037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">頑鈍＝殘頑【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769037"><lem wit="【大】">頑鈍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">殘頑</rdg></app>
<lb n="0769c04" ed="T"/>如前。<note n="0769038" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">經＝連【三】【宮】</note><note n="0769038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">經＝連【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769038"><lem wit="【大】">經</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">連</rdg></app>五百世。重罪乃畢。後乃為人。常有
<lb n="0769c05" ed="T"/>頭痛之患。世尊重曰。<app source="0769004" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">鶖露</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">秋露</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">鶖鷺</rdg></app>子。夫人處世。不
<lb n="0769c06" ed="T"/><note n="0769039" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">惟＝唯【三】【宮】</note><note n="0769039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">惟＝唯【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769039"><lem wit="【大】">惟</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">唯</rdg></app>忍者。所生之處。不值佛世。違法遠僧。常
<lb n="0769c07" ed="T"/>在三<note n="0769040" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">塗＝途【宮】</note><app n="0769040"><lem wit="【大】">塗</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">途</rdg></app>。終而復始。輒有劫數。若蒙餘福。得
<lb n="0769c08" ed="T"/>出為人。稟操常愚。&CB00191;虐自隨。乃心嫉聖。謗
<lb n="0769c09" ed="T"/>毀至尊。為人醜陋。眾所惡憎。生輒貧窮。<note n="0769041" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">仕＝士【三】【宮】</note><note n="0769041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">仕＝士【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769041"><lem wit="【大】">仕</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">士</rdg></app>
<lb n="0769c10" ed="T"/>不得官。願與<note n="0769042" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">意＝福【三】【宮】</note><note n="0769042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">意＝福【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769042"><lem wit="【大】">意</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">福</rdg></app>違。天神聖賢。所不祐助。夜
<lb n="0769c11" ed="T"/>常惡夢。妖怪首尾。飛禍縱橫。所處不寧。心
<lb n="0769c12" ed="T"/>常恐怖。斯之所由。由不忍伏。<note n="0769043" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔惡心〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0769043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔惡心〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769043"><lem wit="【大】">惡心</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>故使然
<lb n="0769c13" ed="T"/>耳。忍惡行者。所生常安。眾禍消滅。願輒如
<lb n="0769c14" ed="T"/>志。顏貌煒曄。身強少病。財<note n="0769044" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">榮尊貴＝福榮尊【三】【宮】</note><note n="0769044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">榮尊貴＝福榮尊【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769044"><lem wit="【大】">榮尊貴</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">福榮尊</rdg></app>。皆由忍
<lb n="0769c15" ed="T"/>辱慈<note n="0769045" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">惠＝慧【宮】</note><app n="0769045"><lem wit="【大】">惠</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">慧</rdg></app>濟眾之所致也。忍<note n="0769046" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">之＝便【三】【宮】</note><note n="0769046" resp="CBETA" type="mod">之＝便【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769046"><lem wit="【大】">之</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">便</rdg></app>為福。身安親
<lb n="0769c16" ed="T"/>寧。宗家<note n="0769047" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">和興＝餘慶【三】【宮】</note><note n="0769047" resp="CBETA" type="mod">和興＝餘慶【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769047"><lem wit="【大】">和興</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">餘慶</rdg></app>。未嘗不歡。智者深見。<note n="0769048" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">迮＝敬【三】【宮】</note><note n="0769048" resp="CBETA" type="mod">迮＝敬【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769048"><lem wit="【大】">迮</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">敬</rdg></app><note n="0769049" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">伏＋（安親寧宗）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0769049" resp="CBETA" type="mod">伏＋（安親寧宗）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769049"><lem wit="【大】">伏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">伏安親寧宗</rdg></app>
<lb n="0769c17" ed="T"/>其心。<note n="0769050" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">心＝惡【明】</note><app n="0769050"><lem wit="【大】">心</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">惡</rdg></app>者誤人破家危身<note n="0769051" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">王法＝為王【三】【宮】</note><note n="0769051" resp="CBETA" type="mod">王法＝為王【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769051"><lem wit="【大】">王法</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">為王</rdg></app>所戮。地獄
<lb n="0769c18" ed="T"/>燒煮。或為餓鬼。亦為畜生。皆心之過也。世
<lb n="0769c19" ed="T"/>尊又曰。寧<note n="0769052" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">以＝臥【三】【宮】</note><note n="0769052" resp="CBETA" type="mod">以＝臥【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769052"><lem wit="【大】">以</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">臥</rdg></app>利劍貫腹截肌。自投火中。慎
<lb n="0769c20" ed="T"/>無履惡。寧戴須彌。<note n="0769053" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">迮＝奪【三】【宮】</note><note n="0769053" resp="CBETA" type="mod">迮＝奪【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769053"><lem wit="【大】">迮</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">奪</rdg></app>毀其命。投于巨海。魚
<lb n="0769c21" ed="T"/>鱉所吞。慎無為惡矣。不知其義。慎無妄言。
<lb n="0769c22" ed="T"/>佛之明法。與俗相背。俗之所珍。道<note n="0769054" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">之＝大【三】【宮】</note><note n="0769054" resp="CBETA" type="mod">之＝大【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0769054"><lem wit="【大】">之</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">大</rdg></app>所賤。
<lb n="0769c23" ed="T"/>清濁異流。明愚異趣。忠&CB00126;相&CB00677;。邪常嫉正。
<pb n="0770a" id="T14.0500.0770a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0770a01" ed="T"/>故<note n="0770001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">嗜＝著【三】【宮】</note><note n="0770001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">嗜＝著【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0770001"><lem wit="【大】">嗜</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">著</rdg></app>欲之人。不好我無慾之行也。寧<note n="0770002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">吞＝嗒【宮】</note><app n="0770002"><lem wit="【大】">吞</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">嗒</rdg></app>然
<lb n="0770a02" ed="T"/>炭。無謗三尊。忍之為明。踰於日月。龍象之
<lb n="0770a03" ed="T"/>力。可謂盛猛。比之於忍。萬萬不如一。七寶
<lb n="0770a04" ed="T"/>之<note n="0770003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">燿＝嚮【三】【宮】</note><note n="0770003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">燿＝嚮【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0770003"><lem wit="【大】">燿</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">嚮</rdg></app>。凡俗所貴。然其招憂。以致災患。忍之
<lb n="0770a05" ed="T"/>為寶。終始獲安。布施十方。雖有大福。福不
<lb n="0770a06" ed="T"/>如<note n="0770004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">忍＝也【三】【宮】</note><note n="0770004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">忍＝也【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0770004"><lem wit="【大】">忍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">也</rdg></app>。懷忍行<note n="0770005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">慈＝慧【宋】【元】【宮】，惠【明】</note><note n="0770005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">慈＝慧【宋】【元】【宮】，＝惠【明】</note><app n="0770005"><lem wit="【大】">慈</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】">慧</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">惠</rdg></app>。世世無怨。中心恬然。<note n="0770006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">終＝眾【三】【宮】</note><note n="0770006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">終＝眾【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0770006"><lem wit="【大】">終</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">眾</rdg></app>
<lb n="0770a07" ed="T"/>無毒害。世無所怙。唯忍可恃。忍為安宅。災
<lb n="0770a08" ed="T"/>怪不生。忍為神鎧。眾兵不加。忍為大<note n="0770007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">舟＝身【宮】</note><app n="0770007"><lem wit="【大】">舟</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">身</rdg></app>。可
<lb n="0770a09" ed="T"/>以渡難。忍為良藥。能濟眾命。忍者之志。何
<lb n="0770a10" ed="T"/>願不獲。若欲願為飛行皇帝典四天下第二
<lb n="0770a11" ed="T"/><note n="0770008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">天＋（天）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0770008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">天＋（天）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0770008"><lem wit="【大】">天</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">天天</rdg></app>帝釋。及上第六天。壽命無極身體香潔。
<lb n="0770a12" ed="T"/>所願自然。猶若家物<note n="0770009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">取之＝所之【宮】</note><app n="0770009"><lem wit="【大】">取之</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">所之</rdg></app>。即得志願。清淨
<lb n="0770a13" ed="T"/>沙門四道。求之可得。在己所向。吾今得佛。諸
<lb n="0770a14" ed="T"/>天所宗。獨步三界。忍力所致。佛告諸沙門。當
<lb n="0770a15" ed="T"/>誦忍經無忘。須臾懷之識之誦之宣之。當宣
<lb n="0770a16" ed="T"/>忍德以濟眾生。佛說經竟。諸沙門皆大歡喜。
<lb n="0770a17" ed="T"/>作禮而去。</p></div1>
<lb n="0770a18" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="close"><jhead><note n="0770010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（佛說）＋羅【三】【宮】</note><note n="0770010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（佛說）＋羅【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0770010"><lem wit="【大】">羅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">佛說羅</rdg></app>云忍辱<note n="0770011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">經＋（終）【明】</note><app n="0770011"><lem wit="【大】">經</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">經終</rdg></app></jhead></juan>
</body></text></TEI.2>